      "content": "Combining sertraline with St. John's Wort is generally not recommended because both substances can affect serotonin levels in your brain. This combination carries a significant risk of a serious side effect called serotonin syndrome. Please discuss this with your prescribing doctor before making any changes to your medication or adding supplements to manage your mood during finals.",
