      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but st johns wort is just a natural herb, right? i was reading online that it's much milder than prescription stuff. i don't feel like i need a doctor for just a supplement, i just want to know if a small dose would be fine to help me get through the next two weeks. i'm not looking to replace the sertraline, just add it in for a bit.",
